SIMPLE: detective
RECORDS: 2

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Detective
<hw>De*tect"ive</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Fitted for, or
skilled in, detecting; employed in detecting crime or criminals; <as>as,
a <ex>detective</ex> officer</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Detective</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Detective
<hw>De*tect"ive</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who business it is so
detect criminals or discover matters of secrecy.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Detector</ent>⟦br⟧
